texture->getGraphicsDataAddress()` double-indirection). `buildSamplerDescForStage0` helper implements CODEX Q3 mapping: `TF_anisotropic` → `D3D11_FILTER_ANISOTROPIC` + clamped aniso; `TF_linear`/`TF_point` direct; `TF_invalid`/cubic/unsafe → linear fallback; `TF_none` mip → point mip; anisotropy clamped to `[1, 16]` per MS docs (no `getMaxAnisotropy` caps query — CODEX Q3a). `apply()` binds via the new state-cache setters; unbinds SRV0 when no slot-0 sampler exists in pass (CODEX Q4 anti-sticky-bleed). Removed Iter-4 misleading `sampler0=NULL` diagnostic in `selectFallbackPSForVS`; replaced with 4 lifetime counters across `StaticShaderData::remove()` + `StateCache::remove()` shutdown logs (passesTotal / passesWithSampler0 / passesWithSampler0TextureResolved / drawsWithSRV0Bound). Build: 5-target MSBuild EXIT=0; one C4701 surfaced mid-build (uninitialized-textureData on `m_textureTag == 0` branch) — fixed by always pre-filling defaults before `getTextureData`; final rebuild 0 new C-warnings beyond pre-existing DirectXMath C4459 / MSB8012 baseline, 0 errors. **Kenny smoke (2026-05-22 ~10:18): visible-textured-Tatooine confirmed; world shows Tatooine color palette; audio fires post-world-load; scattered magenta triangles throughout but NOT spatially split — pure expected residue from VSes lacking TEXCOORD0 (real Phase 12 asset re-author territory: vertex-color-only UI / particles / debug lines / non-UV coordinate generation).** Counter capture unavailable (DEBUG_REPORT_LOG_PRINT goes to OutputDebugString + stdout per Plan 11-09.13 Iter-3 finding; lost on explorer-launched smokes). Plan 11-09 + 11-09.5/6/7/8/9/10/11/12/13 milestones preserved. Plan 11-10 (DPVS remeasurement) + Plan 11-11 (visual-parity verdict + Phase 11 SUMMARY) now genuinely unblocked. CODEX consult preserved at `11-09.14-CODEX-CONSULT-srv0-per-pass-texture-binding.md` (Bucket A verdict + 2 corrections + Q1..Q6 specifics). Commits: `0a89819f3` (Iter-1 feat) → `98902b712` (iteration-log hash fill). — r