.planning\phases\11-d3d11-renderer-plugin\11-09-CODEX-CONSULT-iter2-magenta-missing.md:20:Compile path: `compilePixelShaderFromHlsl` helper (Plan 11-05; first real caller is Iter-2) → optional shader-cache `tryLoad` → `Direct3d11_HlslRewrite::applyToMainSource` → `D3DCompile` (profile `ps_4_0_level_9_3`; flags D3DCOMPILE_DEBUG | D3DCOMPILE_SKIP_OPTIMIZATION | D3DCOMPILE_ENABLE_BACKWARDS_COMPATIBILITY | D3DCOMPILE_PACK_MATRIX_ROW_MAJOR) → unconditional `Direct3d11_Device::getDevice()->CreatePixelShader` → returns true. `install()` FATALs if helper returns false OR if `ms_fallbackPS` is empty afterward.
