.planning\phases\11-d3d11-renderer-plugin\11-09.14-CODEX-CONSULT-srv0-per-pass-texture-binding.md:57:- `Pass::apply()` (`.cpp:820+`) handles VS bind + material → cbuffer constants + textureFactor + textureScroll + alpha test + stencil + fog + … and finally iterates `Stages`, calling `Stage::apply(stage_index)` on each.
