.planning\phases\11-d3d11-renderer-plugin\11-09.15-CODEX-CONSULT-fonts-invisible-splash-desat.md:55:Stage 0 texture binding is handled by `Direct3d11_StaticShaderData::construct` (line 316–447) — it walks `pass->m_pixelShader->m_textureSamplers`, finds the entry with `m_textureIndex == 0`, resolves via `shader.getTextureData(tag, ...)` or `Direct3d11_TextureData::getGlobalTexture(tag)`, and stores the SRV in `m_passStage0[passIndex].m_texture`. `apply(passNumber)` binds that SRV to slot 0 and the matching sampler. **Slots 1–7 are NOT bound** — Bucket A scope (Plan 11-09.14) was deliberately slot-0-only.
